column8: Each GotM and RPGotQ game you complete gains you 1 point and each GotW game you complete gives you .5 points. You may complete as many games as you like for each month.
3$ Patron = 1 point per month, 5$/CHAMPION = 2, and LEGEND = 3.
Completing any Game of the Year Awards game at any point in 2023 earns you one point.
The Leaderboard is ranked by points earned through GotM, GotW, GotY, and RPGotQ; being ONLY a Patron won't rank you highly.
Have fun! This spreadsheet is maintained by Rapid99. Message him on Discord should you notice any issues or have any questions.
